WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.740 line:80%
=Episode 35=

00:01:39.340 --> 00:01:40.180 line:80%
Mother.

00:01:40.290 --> 00:01:41.130 line:80%
Impossible.

00:01:41.290 --> 00:01:42.780 line:80%
Father would never use me to practice.

00:01:43.130 --> 00:01:44.130 line:80%
He's my father.

00:01:45.130 --> 00:01:45.980 line:80%
It's Cai Zhao's fault.

00:01:46.490 --> 00:01:47.390 line:80%
She's talking nonsense.

00:01:47.400 --> 00:01:48.340 line:80%
Let's just ignore her.

00:01:49.620 --> 00:01:51.490 line:80%
Your grandfather once said

00:01:52.320 --> 00:01:54.010 line:80%
he couldn't bear to part with his daughter.

00:01:54.700 --> 00:01:55.540 line:80%
So,

00:01:56.370 --> 00:01:57.900 line:80%
he'd never become the greatest.

00:01:59.730 --> 00:02:01.090 line:80%
So that's why.

00:02:08.530 --> 00:02:09.370 line:80%
Zhao.

00:02:09.530 --> 00:02:10.620 line:80%
I'm begging you.

00:02:11.340 --> 00:02:13.410 line:80%
You must protect Lingbo.

00:02:14.620 --> 00:02:15.810 line:80%
Take her to Luoying Valley,

00:02:16.590 --> 00:02:17.700 line:80%
or even to the demonic sect.

00:02:19.140 --> 00:02:20.580 line:80%
Anywhere.

00:02:24.650 --> 00:02:26.650 line:80%
Just keep her safe.

00:02:28.900 --> 00:02:30.620 line:80%
I'm begging you.

00:02:30.620 --> 00:02:31.460 line:80%
Mother.

00:02:31.930 --> 00:02:32.770 line:80%
Lady Yin.

00:02:43.020 --> 00:02:43.930 line:80%
Mother.

00:02:44.900 --> 00:02:45.930 line:80%
Lingbo, be good.

00:02:47.930 --> 00:02:49.620 line:80%
Go hide for a while.

00:02:50.210 --> 00:02:51.690 line:80%
Wait for this to pass.

00:02:52.340 --> 00:02:53.180 line:80%
It'll be fine.

00:02:54.650 --> 00:02:55.580 line:80%
Mother.

00:02:58.810 --> 00:03:00.210 line:80%
What's happening to you?

00:03:02.490 --> 00:03:03.330 line:80%
I'm not leaving.

00:03:04.020 --> 00:03:05.530 line:80%
I'm not going anywhere.

00:03:08.180 --> 00:03:09.690 line:80%
Don't frighten me.

00:03:10.210 --> 00:03:11.050 line:80%
Mother.

00:03:12.210 --> 00:03:13.050 line:80%
Lady Yin.

00:03:14.490 --> 00:03:16.460 line:80%
The Qingque Sect is on high alert.

00:03:17.780 --> 00:03:19.340 line:80%
If Lingbo hadn't helped me,

00:03:20.140 --> 00:03:21.460 line:80%
I couldn't have entered here.

00:03:23.810 --> 00:03:26.210 line:80%
Please tell me where the secret passage is.

00:03:28.020 --> 00:03:29.140 line:80%
I'll get Lingbo out safely.

00:03:33.780 --> 00:03:34.620 line:80%
Come with me.

00:03:39.620 --> 00:03:40.460 line:80%
Madam.

00:03:40.650 --> 00:03:41.580 line:80%
Lord Qi is here.

00:04:07.140 --> 00:04:07.980 line:80%
Yunke.

00:04:09.300 --> 00:04:11.340 line:80%
Aren't you busy with the demon sect?

00:04:11.780 --> 00:04:12.930 line:80%
Why come here then?

00:04:13.740 --> 00:04:14.580 line:80%
Where's Lingbo?

00:04:15.140 --> 00:04:17.700 line:80%
Isn't she in her room?

00:04:21.020 --> 00:04:22.020 line:80%
Zhao has been here?

00:04:22.530 --> 00:04:23.370 line:80%
Zhao?

00:04:24.940 --> 00:04:26.020 line:80%
I don't know what you mean.

00:04:26.530 --> 00:04:27.700 line:80%
Since you know,

00:04:28.610 --> 00:04:29.700 line:80%
I won't explain further.

00:04:30.500 --> 00:04:31.340 line:80%
Bring Lingbo out.

00:04:31.820 --> 00:04:32.850 line:80%
She'll be willing

00:04:33.290 --> 00:04:34.380 line:80%
to help her father

00:04:34.660 --> 00:04:35.780 line:80%
fulfill his great ambition.

00:04:37.900 --> 00:04:38.740 line:80%
Qi Yunke.

00:04:39.340 --> 00:04:41.410 line:80%
How dare you call yourself her father?

00:04:41.410 --> 00:04:42.850 line:80%
How could you be so heartless?

00:04:42.850 --> 00:04:44.650 line:80%
Lingbo is your flesh and blood.

00:04:45.020 --> 00:04:46.780 line:80%
Seems Zhao came here.

00:04:47.370 --> 00:04:48.620 line:80%
Wenxun, there's a passage.

00:04:48.640 --> 00:04:49.420 line:80%
Go and stop them.

00:04:53.650 --> 00:04:54.650 line:80%
You must not go.

00:04:56.170 --> 00:04:57.010 line:80%
Keep an eye on her.

00:04:57.140 --> 00:04:57.980 line:80%
Lady Yin.

00:04:58.290 --> 00:04:59.170 line:80%
At this point,

00:04:59.500 --> 00:05:00.650 line:80%
you should heed the master.

00:05:05.610 --> 00:05:06.450 line:80%
Dalou.

00:05:07.020 --> 00:05:07.860 line:80%
The one

00:05:08.820 --> 00:05:10.900 line:80%
you cherish most is Lingbo.

00:05:11.780 --> 00:05:13.380 line:80%
Now they want Lingbo dead.

00:05:13.380 --> 00:05:14.580 line:80%
Stop them at once.

00:05:14.580 --> 00:05:16.090 line:80%
Stop them.

00:05:21.370 --> 00:05:22.210 line:80%
Qi Yunke.

00:05:22.210 --> 00:05:23.410 line:80%
Have you lost your mind?

00:05:24.020 --> 00:05:25.580 line:80%
Lingbo carries your bloodline.

00:05:25.580 --> 00:05:27.380 line:80%
She's also Yin family's blood.

00:05:28.290 --> 00:05:29.130 line:80%
She can only

00:05:30.210 --> 00:05:31.780 line:80%
blame her bad fate

00:05:32.210 --> 00:05:34.020 line:80%
to be Yin Dai's granddaughter.

00:05:34.410 --> 00:05:36.530 line:80%
You hate my father that much?

00:05:37.090 --> 00:05:38.290 line:80%
Of course I do.

00:05:39.780 --> 00:05:40.840 line:80%
Let me tell you the truth.

00:05:42.050 --> 00:05:44.210 line:80%
Back then, I revealed his whereabouts

00:05:44.210 --> 00:05:46.170 line:80%
to Zhao Tianba and Han Yisu.

00:05:46.820 --> 00:05:47.660 line:80%
It was also me

00:05:48.020 --> 00:05:50.020 line:80%
who drugged his guards.

00:05:50.020 --> 00:05:51.780 line:80%
So in the fierce battle,

00:05:51.780 --> 00:05:52.940 line:80%
they lost their strength.

00:05:53.380 --> 00:05:54.650 line:80%
Qi Yunke!

00:06:04.060 --> 00:06:04.980 line:80%
No one in the passage.

00:06:11.900 --> 00:06:12.820 line:80%
Where did they go?

00:06:15.650 --> 00:06:17.050 line:80%
Give it up.

00:06:18.090 --> 00:06:20.170 line:80%
You'll never find them.

00:06:42.050 --> 00:06:42.890 line:80%
My dear.

00:06:43.140 --> 00:06:44.500 line:80%
Security is tight here.

00:06:44.940 --> 00:06:46.090 line:80%
Where are you going?

00:06:55.380 --> 00:06:56.610 line:80%
Madam, run!

00:06:59.850 --> 00:07:00.690 line:80%
Nanny.

00:07:01.210 --> 00:07:02.050 line:80%
Nanny!

00:07:03.850 --> 00:07:04.730 line:80%
Nanny.

00:07:05.410 --> 00:07:06.580 line:80%
Nanny.

00:07:09.170 --> 00:07:10.820 line:80%
Run.

00:07:19.050 --> 00:07:19.890 line:80%
Sulian.

00:07:21.530 --> 00:07:23.170 line:80%
If you go back quietly,

00:07:24.090 --> 00:07:25.210 line:80%
you can still be

00:07:25.210 --> 00:07:27.210 line:80%
the honored Lady of Qingque Sect.

00:07:28.380 --> 00:07:29.340 line:80%
Why?

00:07:31.610 --> 00:07:33.090 line:80%
Why are you doing this to me?

00:07:47.650 --> 00:07:48.730 line:80%
Qi Yunke.

00:07:50.410 --> 00:07:52.410 line:80%
Do I mean nothing

00:07:52.410 --> 00:07:54.410 line:80%
to you at all?

00:07:57.290 --> 00:07:59.500 line:80%
I remember the first time I met you.

00:08:00.140 --> 00:08:01.170 line:80%
You came down the mountain

00:08:02.380 --> 00:08:05.650 line:80%
to give money and food to the poor.

00:08:06.050 --> 00:08:07.850 line:80%
Back then, I thought,

00:08:09.500 --> 00:08:11.700 line:80%
I was looking at a fairy.

00:08:12.820 --> 00:08:13.780 line:80%
Your father was

00:08:13.780 --> 00:08:16.850 line:80%
the greatest hero under heaven.

00:08:16.850 --> 00:08:17.690 line:80%
I was just

00:08:19.200 --> 00:08:20.050 line:80%
an ignorant boy

00:08:20.050 --> 00:08:22.650 line:80%
from a poor widow's family.

00:08:23.660 --> 00:08:24.500 line:80%
When your father

00:08:24.500 --> 00:08:26.290 line:80%
wanted to take me as his disciple,

00:08:26.900 --> 00:08:28.700 line:80%
Pingshu did have concerns.

00:08:28.700 --> 00:08:30.460 line:80%
But I couldn't afford to think so much.

00:08:31.780 --> 00:08:34.220 line:80%
To study under the master I adore,

00:08:34.220 --> 00:08:36.500 line:80%
to be near the fairy in my heart...

00:08:36.500 --> 00:08:38.020 line:80%
these were things an ignorant boy

00:08:38.020 --> 00:08:40.450 line:80%
could only dream of.

00:08:41.650 --> 00:08:42.490 line:80%
But the dream

00:08:43.170 --> 00:08:44.620 line:80%
ended all too soon.

00:08:47.530 --> 00:08:49.290 line:80%
That so-called greatest hero

00:08:50.140 --> 00:08:52.140 line:80%
was nothing but a vile man.

00:08:52.780 --> 00:08:54.050 line:80%
And you, the fairy,

00:08:54.410 --> 00:08:56.620 line:80%
were nothing but narrow, shallow,

00:08:56.620 --> 00:08:58.450 line:80%
and greedy.

00:09:02.020 --> 00:09:03.570 line:80%
Your father told me

00:09:04.690 --> 00:09:08.020 line:80%
a sect leader can't rely
only on righteousness.

00:09:08.740 --> 00:09:10.690 line:80%
One hand in light, one cloaked in shade.

00:09:11.220 --> 00:09:13.860 line:80%
Only then can you control everything.

00:09:13.860 --> 00:09:15.410 line:80%
And so, like him,

00:09:15.410 --> 00:09:17.650 line:80%
I bred countless shadow guards
and death-sworn.

00:09:18.860 --> 00:09:19.780 line:80%
And you...

00:09:20.810 --> 00:09:22.410 line:80%
When I decided to go to Mount Tu

00:09:22.900 --> 00:09:24.620 line:80%
to help Pingshu,

00:09:24.620 --> 00:09:26.290 line:80%
you brought me that cup of tea.

00:09:27.140 --> 00:09:28.380 line:80%
It kept me asleep

00:09:29.410 --> 00:09:31.500 line:80%
for six whole hours.

00:09:32.220 --> 00:09:33.060 line:80%
And because of that,

00:09:33.860 --> 00:09:35.140 line:80%
Pingshu returned gravely wounded.

00:09:35.450 --> 00:09:37.220 line:80%
If you cared so deeply for Cai Pingshu,

00:09:37.780 --> 00:09:39.290 line:80%
why didn't you marry her?

00:09:39.900 --> 00:09:41.170 line:80%
Why did you marry me?

00:09:41.690 --> 00:09:42.780 line:80%
You vulgar woman.

00:09:43.780 --> 00:09:45.620 line:80%
You only have such petty thoughts.

00:09:47.220 --> 00:09:48.140 line:80%
In your heart,

00:09:48.740 --> 00:09:51.100 line:80%
there's nothing but affairs
between men and women.

00:09:52.140 --> 00:09:53.620 line:80%
But Pingshu and I were different.

00:09:54.900 --> 00:09:55.740 line:80%
She and I

00:09:56.450 --> 00:09:58.220 line:80%
swore before the gods

00:09:58.220 --> 00:09:59.930 line:80%
to be righteous heroes.

00:10:01.100 --> 00:10:02.740 line:80%
For the people of the world,

00:10:02.740 --> 00:10:03.900 line:80%
to help the suffering,

00:10:03.900 --> 00:10:05.450 line:80%
to turn the tide of chaos,

00:10:05.450 --> 00:10:06.510 line:80%
to uphold justice,

00:10:06.530 --> 00:10:08.000 line:80%
to punish the wicked and aid the weak.

00:10:08.020 --> 00:10:09.200 line:80%
So every grievance is answered

00:10:09.230 --> 00:10:10.780 line:80%
and everyone can make their mark.

00:10:10.780 --> 00:10:11.930 line:80%
With chivalry in our hearts,

00:10:11.930 --> 00:10:13.050 line:80%
to drive away evil.

00:10:13.050 --> 00:10:13.980 line:80%
Enough.

00:10:15.290 --> 00:10:17.780 line:80%
If Cai Pingshu knew what you've done,

00:10:17.780 --> 00:10:19.330 line:80%
she would never forgive you.

00:10:23.690 --> 00:10:24.900 line:80%
Pingshu!

00:10:46.170 --> 00:10:47.780 line:80%
But she is gone.

00:10:49.650 --> 00:10:50.500 line:80%
And I

00:10:52.170 --> 00:10:53.500 line:80%
died long ago.

00:10:55.050 --> 00:10:56.620 line:80%
All thanks to your father

00:10:56.620 --> 00:10:57.810 line:80%
and your sister,

00:10:58.530 --> 00:11:00.500 line:80%
plotting step by step.

00:11:10.900 --> 00:11:12.050 line:80%
How ridiculous.

00:11:13.530 --> 00:11:16.170 line:80%
Are you any different from my father now?

00:11:16.810 --> 00:11:18.740 line:80%
All for your own desire,

00:11:19.140 --> 00:11:20.690 line:80%
without caring who dies.

00:11:22.740 --> 00:11:24.810 line:80%
You're exactly the same.

00:11:32.220 --> 00:11:33.060 line:80%
Mother.

00:11:33.620 --> 00:11:34.460 line:80%
Mother.

00:11:38.930 --> 00:11:39.980 line:80%
I only regret

00:11:40.860 --> 00:11:42.690 line:80%
that my skills were lacking.

00:11:43.690 --> 00:11:45.450 line:80%
I couldn't avenge

00:11:46.140 --> 00:11:47.380 line:80%
my father.

00:11:49.100 --> 00:11:50.050 line:80%
Didn't expect

00:11:51.330 --> 00:11:53.100 line:80%
you to have some backbone.

00:11:55.410 --> 00:11:57.100 line:80%
I'll ask you one last time.

00:11:57.100 --> 00:11:58.500 line:80%
Where is Lingbo?

00:12:03.780 --> 00:12:04.620 line:80%
Fine.

00:12:25.020 --> 00:12:27.220 line:80%
Mother.

00:12:28.780 --> 00:12:31.860 line:80%
Mother.

00:13:35.220 --> 00:13:36.220 line:80%
Spread the word.

00:13:38.330 --> 00:13:41.450 line:80%
Demonic rebels
infiltrated Double Lotus Palace.

00:13:42.570 --> 00:13:44.450 line:80%
My wife and daughter

00:13:46.620 --> 00:13:47.900 line:80%
were both killed.

00:13:49.050 --> 00:13:49.890 line:80%
Yes.

00:14:23.650 --> 00:14:24.500 line:80%
Lady Yin.

00:14:37.500 --> 00:14:38.410 line:80%
Lingbo.

00:14:46.410 --> 00:14:47.980 line:80%
I must avenge my mother.

00:14:47.980 --> 00:14:49.530 line:80%
- Lingbo.
- Let go.

00:14:49.530 --> 00:14:51.050 line:80%
I must avenge my mother.

00:14:52.740 --> 00:14:53.900 line:80%
Your mother died saving you.

00:14:54.370 --> 00:14:55.570 line:80%
Do you want her to die in vain?

00:14:56.030 --> 00:14:57.650 line:80%
Let's find a way down the mountain first.

00:15:16.450 --> 00:15:17.570 line:80%
I'll hold them off.

00:15:17.570 --> 00:15:18.650 line:80%
Find somewhere to hide.

00:15:18.650 --> 00:15:20.140 line:80%
When Xingjia sees we didn't return,

00:15:20.140 --> 00:15:21.410 line:80%
he'll alert the others.

00:15:21.410 --> 00:15:22.330 line:80%
You can come out then.

00:15:22.330 --> 00:15:23.170 line:80%
No.

00:16:00.650 --> 00:16:01.780 line:80%
Everyone stop!

00:16:07.930 --> 00:16:08.980 line:80%
Li Wenxun.

00:16:09.380 --> 00:16:11.930 line:80%
Qi Yunke need me alive

00:16:11.930 --> 00:16:13.980 line:80%
to practice the Ziwei Method, right?

00:16:14.500 --> 00:16:15.620 line:80%
Let Cai Zhao go.

00:16:16.170 --> 00:16:17.930 line:80%
Or I'll die right here.

00:16:18.450 --> 00:16:19.780 line:80%
Qi Yunke will never

00:16:19.780 --> 00:16:21.170 line:80%
master the Ziwei Method.

00:16:21.170 --> 00:16:22.380 line:80%
No, Lingbo.

00:16:24.530 --> 00:16:25.370 line:80%
Cai Zhao.

00:16:25.900 --> 00:16:27.220 line:80%
I'm your senior.

00:16:27.530 --> 00:16:29.450 line:80%
Why do you always play the hero?

00:16:30.140 --> 00:16:31.860 line:80%
This time it's my turn.

00:16:36.980 --> 00:16:38.100 line:80%
Go.

00:16:50.690 --> 00:16:52.740 line:80%
Take her back. Lord Qi's training matters.

00:17:19.740 --> 00:17:21.130 line:80%
You're exhausted and drained.

00:17:21.660 --> 00:17:23.090 line:80%
Take the top gold pill.

00:17:43.090 --> 00:17:44.020 line:80%
Uncle Lei.

00:17:46.420 --> 00:17:48.810 line:80%
You knew what Master was doing,

00:17:49.660 --> 00:17:50.500 line:80%
didn't you?

00:17:51.780 --> 00:17:52.780 line:80%
Does it matter

00:17:53.180 --> 00:17:54.090 line:80%
whether I knew?

00:17:54.500 --> 00:17:56.890 line:80%
The Qingque Sect belongs
to your master now.

00:17:58.180 --> 00:17:59.460 line:80%
What can we do?

00:18:00.810 --> 00:18:02.090 line:80%
Do you think

00:18:02.810 --> 00:18:04.180 line:80%
Master is right?

00:18:04.180 --> 00:18:05.850 line:80%
Don't you hate Yin Dai?

00:18:05.850 --> 00:18:07.890 line:80%
Don't you want revenge for your aunt?

00:18:08.420 --> 00:18:09.740 line:80%
Of course I hate Yin Dai.

00:18:20.290 --> 00:18:22.530 line:80%
But this isn't the path of vengeance.

00:18:26.330 --> 00:18:27.500 line:80%
Uncle Chang,

00:18:28.290 --> 00:18:29.610 line:80%
Lord Song,

00:18:31.180 --> 00:18:32.180 line:80%
Uncle Zhou,

00:18:33.660 --> 00:18:34.980 line:80%
and Lingbo,

00:18:37.500 --> 00:18:38.890 line:80%
what wrong have they done?

00:18:42.180 --> 00:18:43.090 line:80%
It's too late now.

00:18:44.940 --> 00:18:46.050 line:80%
Nothing can be undone.

00:18:54.330 --> 00:18:55.460 line:80%
Stay here.

00:18:56.090 --> 00:18:57.180 line:80%
He won't hurt you.

00:19:04.020 --> 00:19:04.860 line:80%
Uncle Lei.

00:19:09.220 --> 00:19:10.940 line:80%
Back then my aunt knew

00:19:11.610 --> 00:19:13.660 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng had three years left.

00:19:14.980 --> 00:19:16.500 line:80%
Mu Zhengyang told her.

00:19:19.180 --> 00:19:20.980 line:80%
But she still went to Mount Tu.

00:19:22.290 --> 00:19:24.500 line:80%
Even if she could save just one person,

00:19:26.050 --> 00:19:27.570 line:80%
she'd go without hesitation.

00:19:27.980 --> 00:19:29.530 line:80%
From start to end,

00:19:32.460 --> 00:19:34.090 line:80%
she never regretted it.

00:19:35.810 --> 00:19:38.500 line:80%
Even when bedridden later,

00:19:38.940 --> 00:19:41.940 line:80%
even knowing Yin Dai used her,

00:19:42.780 --> 00:19:44.220 line:80%
she never regretted it.

00:19:51.290 --> 00:19:52.570 line:80%
She once told me,

00:19:56.050 --> 00:19:57.130 line:80%
in this life,

00:20:00.180 --> 00:20:01.850 line:80%
doing what you believe in

00:20:03.980 --> 00:20:05.420 line:80%
is enough.

00:20:16.940 --> 00:20:17.850 line:80%
Pingshu…

00:20:22.940 --> 00:20:24.780 line:80%
My aunt needs no revenge.

00:20:24.780 --> 00:20:26.130 line:80%
Nor does she need Master

00:20:26.130 --> 00:20:27.890 line:80%
to slaughter in her name.

00:20:29.740 --> 00:20:30.700 line:80%
What she wanted

00:20:35.850 --> 00:20:37.850 line:80%
was a peaceful Jianghu.

00:20:42.420 --> 00:20:43.780 line:80%
If she were alive,

00:20:49.020 --> 00:20:50.700 line:80%
she would stop Master.

00:21:13.610 --> 00:21:15.220 line:80%
Yuzhi's locked in the Discipline Hall.

00:21:16.050 --> 00:21:18.700 line:80%
Dai Fengchi and the others,
the back mountain dungeon.

00:21:19.130 --> 00:21:20.570 line:80%
The antidote to the softening powder.

00:21:23.020 --> 00:21:24.330 line:80%
Go and free them.

00:21:46.740 --> 00:21:47.850 line:80%
Thank you, Uncle Lei.

00:22:16.570 --> 00:22:17.500 line:80%
Pingshu.

00:22:18.850 --> 00:22:20.120 line:80%
This time,

00:22:21.010 --> 00:22:22.360 line:80%
did I do the right thing?

00:22:24.020 --> 00:22:26.660 line:80%
(Righteous Spirit)
In Jianghu, strength rules.

00:22:28.050 --> 00:22:29.460 line:80%
But words mean nothing

00:22:30.050 --> 00:22:32.610 line:80%
beside supreme power.

00:22:33.330 --> 00:22:34.370 line:80%
As long as the three of us

00:22:34.780 --> 00:22:36.090 line:80%
perfect our skills,

00:22:36.090 --> 00:22:37.780 line:80%
we'll form a triangle of power

00:22:38.090 --> 00:22:39.940 line:80%
and fear no one.

00:22:40.330 --> 00:22:41.170 line:80%
Agreed.

00:22:42.050 --> 00:22:42.980 line:80%
In that case,

00:22:43.420 --> 00:22:45.220 line:80%
we'll guard you while you train.

00:22:45.740 --> 00:22:46.890 line:80%
Once you succeed,

00:22:47.290 --> 00:22:49.370 line:80%
share the secret with us.

00:22:49.700 --> 00:22:51.290 line:80%
If you break your word,

00:22:51.980 --> 00:22:54.370 line:80%
I'll give up the Guangtian Sect throne

00:22:54.370 --> 00:22:56.660 line:80%
and expose you to the world.

00:23:00.420 --> 00:23:02.500 line:80%
When Nie Hengcheng trained back then,

00:23:02.850 --> 00:23:04.460 line:80%
he nearly went berserk.

00:23:04.890 --> 00:23:08.020 line:80%
I merely wished to test it for you.

00:23:08.660 --> 00:23:09.740 line:80%
Would that be acceptable?

00:23:14.180 --> 00:23:15.810 line:80%
Lord Qi, train in peace.

00:23:15.810 --> 00:23:18.020 line:80%
We will guard Fengyun Peak for you.

00:23:20.020 --> 00:23:21.050 line:80%
I'm grateful to you both.

00:23:36.980 --> 00:23:37.820 line:80%
You really trust him?

00:23:38.530 --> 00:23:40.330 line:80%
At this point, what choice do we have?

00:23:41.130 --> 00:23:42.330 line:80%
News has spread that I killed

00:23:42.660 --> 00:23:44.090 line:80%
my father-in-law's family

00:23:44.090 --> 00:23:45.810 line:80%
to make corpse slaves.

00:23:46.780 --> 00:23:48.020 line:80%
If we don't go all in now,

00:23:48.020 --> 00:23:49.290 line:80%
shall we wait to be judged?

00:23:52.740 --> 00:23:54.330 line:80%
Song Shijun isn't dead yet.

00:23:54.700 --> 00:23:56.570 line:80%
Your seat as Guangtian Sect leader

00:23:56.980 --> 00:23:58.500 line:80%
may not be secure.

00:24:00.850 --> 00:24:01.780 line:80%
Remove one more man,

00:24:02.940 --> 00:24:03.940 line:80%
and it will be.

00:24:09.610 --> 00:24:10.660 line:80%
Two fools.

00:24:11.570 --> 00:24:13.290 line:80%
You're the leader of the six sects.

00:24:13.610 --> 00:24:15.370 line:80%
Why raise two rivals?

00:24:15.370 --> 00:24:16.610 line:80%
They're not fools.

00:24:17.420 --> 00:24:18.460 line:80%
They're greedy.

00:24:18.460 --> 00:24:19.700 line:80%
Greed

00:24:20.420 --> 00:24:21.780 line:80%
blinds them.

00:24:24.570 --> 00:24:25.410 line:80%
Dalou.

00:24:29.290 --> 00:24:30.130 line:80%
What do you think?

00:24:34.570 --> 00:24:37.020 line:80%
I was once an orphaned beggar,

00:24:37.020 --> 00:24:38.530 line:80%
dying by the roadside.

00:24:39.810 --> 00:24:41.740 line:80%
Master and Ms. Cai saved me.

00:24:41.740 --> 00:24:43.050 line:80%
That is why I live today.

00:24:43.050 --> 00:24:44.500 line:80%
Whatever Master does,

00:24:44.500 --> 00:24:46.660 line:80%
I know it is for Ms. Cai.

00:24:46.660 --> 00:24:48.460 line:80%
I'll serve you unto death.

00:24:57.850 --> 00:24:59.090 line:80%
In this world,

00:25:00.220 --> 00:25:02.610 line:80%
few still remember

00:25:03.530 --> 00:25:05.290 line:80%
Pingshu's kindness.

00:25:09.610 --> 00:25:10.450 line:80%
Yunke,

00:25:10.660 --> 00:25:11.940 line:80%
Lingbo's in the secret chamber.

00:25:16.700 --> 00:25:18.700 line:80%
(Righteous Spirit)

00:25:32.780 --> 00:25:34.330 line:80%
Master sent you to kill me?

00:25:34.610 --> 00:25:36.290 line:80%
Don't wrong Qi Yunke.

00:25:37.420 --> 00:25:38.420 line:80%
Your master treats you

00:25:39.500 --> 00:25:41.530 line:80%
like his own child.

00:25:42.530 --> 00:25:44.090 line:80%
This place is so hidden.

00:25:44.700 --> 00:25:46.220 line:80%
If I hadn't followed the food carrier,

00:25:46.610 --> 00:25:47.850 line:80%
I'd never find it.

00:25:48.420 --> 00:25:50.130 line:80%
He could abandon his own daughter,

00:25:51.420 --> 00:25:53.460 line:80%
yet hides you like a treasure.

00:25:53.460 --> 00:25:54.300 line:80%
Sadly,

00:25:55.610 --> 00:25:57.130 line:80%
today's your last day.

00:26:04.530 --> 00:26:05.370 line:80%
Brother.

00:26:06.020 --> 00:26:07.420 line:80%
Do you hate me that much?

00:26:07.890 --> 00:26:09.020 line:80%
Of course I do.

00:26:10.940 --> 00:26:13.050 line:80%
I am the true heir of Guangtian Sect.

00:26:13.050 --> 00:26:15.290 line:80%
Yet everyone only knows you.

00:26:17.220 --> 00:26:18.530 line:80%
You deserve to die.

00:26:34.850 --> 00:26:35.690 line:80%
Cai Zhao?

00:26:36.460 --> 00:26:37.330 line:80%
You dare come here?

00:26:58.980 --> 00:26:59.820 line:80%
Mu Qingyan?

00:27:00.500 --> 00:27:01.370 line:80%
Why are you here?

00:27:03.500 --> 00:27:04.340 line:80%
I protect my own.

00:27:05.290 --> 00:27:06.810 line:80%
Someone hurt my Golden Peng.

00:27:06.810 --> 00:27:08.460 line:80%
Of course I came to see why.

00:27:09.530 --> 00:27:10.500 line:80%
Thank you, Mr. Mu.

00:27:10.940 --> 00:27:12.290 line:80%
And last time at Xuankong Nunnery,

00:27:12.290 --> 00:27:14.220 line:80%
thanks for saving Zhao.

00:27:14.220 --> 00:27:15.570 line:80%
That was for Zhao.

00:27:16.090 --> 00:27:17.290 line:80%
Why thank me, Song?

00:27:19.780 --> 00:27:21.290 line:80%
Enough chatter.

00:27:21.610 --> 00:27:22.890 line:80%
Master has captured Lingbo.

00:27:23.160 --> 00:27:25.160 line:80%
He's about to finish
Ziwei Method's final layer.

00:27:25.420 --> 00:27:26.420 line:80%
We must stop him.

00:27:27.370 --> 00:27:29.180 line:80%
First we must find him.

00:27:29.500 --> 00:27:30.530 line:80%
Where is Qi Yunke?

00:27:31.020 --> 00:27:32.740 line:80%
Wouldn't you know best?

00:27:32.740 --> 00:27:34.020 line:80%
The final layer

00:27:34.020 --> 00:27:35.610 line:80%
is extremely dangerous.

00:27:36.130 --> 00:27:38.130 line:80%
One mistake

00:27:39.050 --> 00:27:40.500 line:80%
and he'll lose control.

00:27:40.500 --> 00:27:41.810 line:80%
So the old tunnels

00:27:42.180 --> 00:27:43.940 line:80%
and unstable chambers can't be used.

00:27:44.370 --> 00:27:45.940 line:80%
He must choose

00:27:45.940 --> 00:27:47.850 line:80%
a place unknown and secure.

00:27:48.070 --> 00:27:48.930 line:80%
Yuzhi.

00:27:49.050 --> 00:27:50.370 line:80%
Did Yin Dai have other chambers?

00:27:50.660 --> 00:27:51.940 line:80%
Grandfather did have

00:27:51.940 --> 00:27:53.940 line:80%
a forbidden training ground full of traps.

00:27:53.940 --> 00:27:54.790 line:80%
Where?

00:27:54.800 --> 00:27:55.680 line:80%
Dusk Palace.

00:27:56.090 --> 00:27:57.020 line:80%
We split up.

00:27:57.700 --> 00:27:58.890 line:80%
This is the antidote.

00:27:59.660 --> 00:28:01.530 line:80%
Go free the imprisoned.

00:28:01.530 --> 00:28:03.170 line:80%
Master's Ziwei Method is nearly complete.

00:28:03.780 --> 00:28:05.080 line:80%
How can just two of you stop him?

00:28:05.080 --> 00:28:05.920 line:80%
Let's go together.

00:28:05.920 --> 00:28:07.370 line:80%
I'll keep Zhao safe.

00:28:07.940 --> 00:28:09.020 line:80%
As for you, Song,

00:28:10.050 --> 00:28:11.660 line:80%
you nearly became a corpse slave

00:28:12.130 --> 00:28:13.940 line:80%
and almost died covering our retreat.

00:28:15.370 --> 00:28:16.210 line:80%
Yuzhi.

00:28:16.940 --> 00:28:17.910 line:80%
Saving them comes first.

00:28:19.370 --> 00:28:20.650 line:80%
Zhao, let's go.

00:28:20.900 --> 00:28:22.370 line:80%
Guanyue is waiting down there.

00:28:22.370 --> 00:28:23.500 line:80%
If he grows impatient,

00:28:23.890 --> 00:28:25.500 line:80%
he might attack the sect.

00:28:26.530 --> 00:28:27.370 line:80%
You brought people?

00:28:28.180 --> 00:28:29.570 line:80%
Do you think the Chief of Li Sect

00:28:29.980 --> 00:28:31.050 line:80%
came alone?

00:28:40.850 --> 00:28:41.980 line:80%
What a coincidence.

00:28:42.850 --> 00:28:44.020 line:80%
Since everyone's here,

00:28:44.330 --> 00:28:45.700 line:80%
let's go up together

00:28:46.020 --> 00:28:47.130 line:80%
and take Fengyun Peak.

00:28:47.400 --> 00:28:48.750 line:80%
Righteous and demonic cannot unite.

00:28:48.780 --> 00:28:49.780 line:80%
Together? Impossible.

00:28:49.850 --> 00:28:52.050 line:80%
Or do you seek to profit from chaos?

00:28:52.500 --> 00:28:53.700 line:80%
Young Lord Zhou,

00:28:53.700 --> 00:28:54.780 line:80%
Lord Zhou was killed

00:28:54.780 --> 00:28:56.530 line:80%
by someone from the six sects.

00:28:56.530 --> 00:28:57.610 line:80%
Young Master came

00:28:57.610 --> 00:28:58.920 line:80%
to help you anyway.

00:28:59.700 --> 00:29:01.420 line:80%
How can you be so blind?

00:29:01.420 --> 00:29:03.020 line:80%
At a time like this,

00:29:03.020 --> 00:29:04.130 line:80%
you're still arguing?

00:29:05.570 --> 00:29:06.410 line:80%
Qi…

00:29:08.180 --> 00:29:09.020 line:80%
Lord Qi

00:29:09.530 --> 00:29:10.660 line:80%
has lost control.

00:29:11.330 --> 00:29:12.890 line:80%
If not stopped in time,

00:29:12.890 --> 00:29:14.420 line:80%
there will be more bloodshed.

00:29:15.090 --> 00:29:16.420 line:80%
At a moment of right and wrong,

00:29:16.420 --> 00:29:17.940 line:80%
both sides must set aside hatred

00:29:17.940 --> 00:29:18.970 line:80%
and fight together.

00:29:19.130 --> 00:29:19.970 line:80%
That's right.

00:29:20.090 --> 00:29:21.220 line:80%
In urgent times, we adapt.

00:29:21.570 --> 00:29:23.020 line:80%
Let's go up together.

00:29:23.610 --> 00:29:24.940 line:80%
But heed my warning.

00:29:25.530 --> 00:29:27.850 line:80%
Qingque Sect guards Beichen.

00:29:29.570 --> 00:29:30.980 line:80%
Do not act rashly.

00:29:31.570 --> 00:29:32.780 line:80%
With Young Master absent,

00:29:33.890 --> 00:29:36.130 line:80%
we follow Luoying Valley's lead.

00:29:36.810 --> 00:29:38.090 line:80%
Young Master must heed

00:29:38.980 --> 00:29:40.460 line:80%
his father-in-law's words.

00:29:42.420 --> 00:29:43.810 line:80%
Very well.

00:29:43.810 --> 00:29:44.700 line:80%
Then let's go up.

00:29:47.330 --> 00:29:48.170 line:80%
Why?

00:29:48.420 --> 00:29:49.530 line:80%
It's Master?

00:29:49.530 --> 00:29:51.090 line:80%
Master was blinded by hatred

00:29:51.740 --> 00:29:52.660 line:80%
and lost his way.

00:29:54.740 --> 00:29:55.580 line:80%
He…

00:29:56.600 --> 00:29:58.020 line:80%
He wants to use Lingbo for training.

00:30:00.570 --> 00:30:02.130 line:80%
Master will use Lingbo to train?

00:30:02.570 --> 00:30:03.410 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:30:03.460 --> 00:30:05.290 line:80%
Zhao and Mr. Mu have gone to save her.

00:30:06.610 --> 00:30:07.780 line:80%
- Lingbo.
- Fengchi.

00:30:07.780 --> 00:30:08.620 line:80%
Lingbo.

00:30:08.850 --> 00:30:10.410 line:80%
- Fengchi.
- Fengchi.

00:30:19.510 --> 00:30:20.980 line:80%
I'm also a disciple of Luoying Valley.

00:30:21.420 --> 00:30:23.220 line:80%
My martial arts are poor,

00:30:23.220 --> 00:30:24.980 line:80%
but training with milady

00:30:24.980 --> 00:30:26.130 line:80%
gave me some inner strength.

00:30:26.660 --> 00:30:27.500 line:80%
Ding,

00:30:27.810 --> 00:30:28.650 line:80%
regulate your breath.

00:30:28.940 --> 00:30:30.260 line:80%
The poison isn't gone yet.

00:30:30.280 --> 00:30:31.450 line:80%
Circulate your qi to expel it.

00:30:34.420 --> 00:30:35.780 line:80%
We have urgent matters now.

00:30:35.780 --> 00:30:36.700 line:80%
We must split up.

00:30:37.850 --> 00:30:39.050 line:80%
The others in the cell

00:30:39.370 --> 00:30:40.210 line:80%
are counting on you.

00:30:41.880 --> 00:30:43.460 line:80%
I must go to Thousandfold Cliff

00:30:43.460 --> 00:30:44.310 line:80%
to release the chains

00:30:44.320 --> 00:30:45.230 line:80%
and let them up.

00:30:45.700 --> 00:30:46.540 line:80%
Wait.

00:30:49.370 --> 00:30:50.500 line:80%
Things are urgent.

00:30:51.260 --> 00:30:52.170 line:80%
I'll fight beside you.

00:30:52.720 --> 00:30:54.020 line:80%
- Your injuries…
- Don't worry.

00:30:54.290 --> 00:30:55.210 line:80%
Saving people

00:30:55.250 --> 00:30:56.470 line:80%
is something I can help with.

00:30:57.290 --> 00:30:58.220 line:80%
Leave it to me.

00:30:59.090 --> 00:31:00.020 line:80%
Be careful.

00:31:20.660 --> 00:31:23.330 line:80%
She was your wife for 20 years.

00:31:27.530 --> 00:31:29.050 line:80%
Why did you kill her?

00:31:33.420 --> 00:31:35.370 line:80%
Because she was Yin Dai's descendant.

00:31:41.220 --> 00:31:43.130 line:80%
Will you kill me too?

00:31:58.020 --> 00:31:58.980 line:80%
You are my daughter.

00:32:00.370 --> 00:32:01.420 line:80%
I won't kill you.

00:32:02.570 --> 00:32:04.220 line:80%
I only need your inner power

00:32:05.570 --> 00:32:07.020 line:80%
to train.

00:32:08.090 --> 00:32:09.050 line:80%
Father does this

00:32:10.020 --> 00:32:11.090 line:80%
for your own good.

00:32:13.020 --> 00:32:14.700 line:80%
Just borrowing my power?

00:32:15.660 --> 00:32:16.500 line:80%
Yes.

00:32:16.850 --> 00:32:17.780 line:80%
Your mother

00:32:18.780 --> 00:32:20.500 line:80%
spoiled you before.

00:32:21.370 --> 00:32:22.500 line:80%
From now on,

00:32:23.500 --> 00:32:25.090 line:80%
I'll teach you himself

00:32:25.940 --> 00:32:27.330 line:80%
and make you worthy.

00:32:29.020 --> 00:32:30.530 line:80%
Don't you want to help me

00:32:31.530 --> 00:32:32.850 line:80%
complete the great cause?

00:32:47.290 --> 00:32:48.180 line:80%
Father.

00:32:53.980 --> 00:32:56.420 line:80%
It's been long
since you spoke to me like this.

00:33:28.610 --> 00:33:29.740 line:80%
Lord Qi's order.

00:33:29.740 --> 00:33:31.250 line:80%
No one may go up the mountain.

00:33:36.570 --> 00:33:37.500 line:80%
Zhuang.

00:33:37.500 --> 00:33:38.340 line:80%
Let him in.

00:33:38.850 --> 00:33:39.690 line:80%
Move aside.

00:33:41.810 --> 00:33:43.290 line:80%
Zhuang, Lord Qi's Master was

00:33:43.310 --> 00:33:45.210 line:80%
the Man in Black
who wiped out the Chang family.

00:33:45.240 --> 00:33:46.460 line:80%
Your master

00:33:46.460 --> 00:33:48.020 line:80%
and Uncle Li were their accomplices.

00:33:48.020 --> 00:33:49.530 line:80%
We were all deceived.

00:33:49.530 --> 00:33:50.370 line:80%
I know.

00:33:50.660 --> 00:33:51.570 line:80%
You knew?

00:33:52.130 --> 00:33:53.330 line:80%
And still helped the villain?

00:33:53.890 --> 00:33:54.730 line:80%
Fan.

00:33:55.090 --> 00:33:57.050 line:80%
I was a useless outer disciple.

00:33:58.130 --> 00:33:59.660 line:80%
Master chose me for the inner sect.

00:33:59.980 --> 00:34:00.980 line:80%
He taught me martial arts

00:34:01.330 --> 00:34:02.460 line:80%
and entrusted me with duties.

00:34:03.610 --> 00:34:04.890 line:80%
I cannot betray his grace.

00:34:14.660 --> 00:34:15.780 line:80%
It must be Yuzhi.

00:34:17.370 --> 00:34:18.850 line:80%
Follow us to Fengyun Peak!

00:34:18.850 --> 00:34:20.410 line:80%
Charge!

00:34:58.890 --> 00:34:59.730 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:35:00.740 --> 00:35:01.740 line:80%
I won't stand here again

00:35:02.450 --> 00:35:04.140 line:80%
watching you walk away.

00:35:07.620 --> 00:35:09.140 line:80%
Mu Qingyan, you…

00:35:09.140 --> 00:35:10.730 line:80%
It's fine. Saving her comes first.

00:35:12.580 --> 00:35:13.720 line:80%
Your poison isn't fully gone.

00:35:13.740 --> 00:35:14.980 line:80%
You can barely protect yourself.

00:35:14.990 --> 00:35:16.830 line:80%
Besides, it's inside
the Six Sects of Beichen.

00:35:16.860 --> 00:35:18.010 line:80%
Don't risk yourself.

00:35:18.010 --> 00:35:19.340 line:80%
But I won't become Mu Zhengyang.

00:35:19.930 --> 00:35:20.850 line:80%
I won't be like him,

00:35:21.450 --> 00:35:22.700 line:80%
cutting off love

00:35:22.700 --> 00:35:23.930 line:80%
for power and greed,

00:35:23.930 --> 00:35:25.930 line:80%
and risking both our lives.

00:35:27.850 --> 00:35:28.690 line:80%
Zhao.

00:35:29.060 --> 00:35:30.010 line:80%
I won't let you follow

00:35:30.010 --> 00:35:31.450 line:80%
your aunt's path.

00:35:34.540 --> 00:35:35.380 line:80%
Come on.

00:35:37.520 --> 00:35:48.180 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:36:06.940 --> 00:36:11.350 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

00:36:11.915 --> 00:36:16.530 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

00:36:16.870 --> 00:36:21.435 line:80%
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

00:36:21.960 --> 00:36:26.260 line:80%
♪Free to wander in the world♪

00:36:29.205 --> 00:36:33.905 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:36:34.430 --> 00:36:38.720 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:36:39.380 --> 00:36:43.410 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:36:43.725 --> 00:36:48.850 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:36:49.425 --> 00:36:54.235 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:36:54.450 --> 00:36:58.620 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:36:59.345 --> 00:37:03.280 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:37:03.780 --> 00:37:09.055 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

